{"type":"text","timestamp":1775900788355,"sessionID":"ses_284125adbffefzbkmrn4NDE8fS","part":{"id":"prt_d7bef4ae7001ec2gelDbFE3W08","messageID":"msg_d7bef18d6001NgARM1enrFxCo4","sessionID":"ses_284125adbffefzbkmrn4NDE8fS","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-043 — Architecture Design and API Documentation\n\n### Documentation Status ✅\n\nAll required documentation is present and comprehensive in `docs/` directory:\n\n- ✅ **Architecture Overview** (`docs/docs/architecture/overview.md`) - Complete system architecture with core components, data flow diagrams, security features, and scalability design\n- ✅ **Data Flow** (`docs/docs/architecture/data-flow.md`) - Detailed request processing, session creation, caching strategies, and message flows\n- ✅ **Module Specifications** (`docs/docs/architecture/modules.md`) - Complete module breakdown with component descriptions, API endpoints, and configuration structures\n- ✅ **API Overview** (`docs/docs/api/overview.md`) - Comprehensive REST API documentation with authentication, error handling, rate limiting, and SDK examples\n\n### Implementation Verification ✅\n\n#### Router Module (`pkg/router/`)\n- ✅ Server implements Gin framework as specified\n- ✅ JWT authentication with RSA key pair management\n- ✅ Session management with caching and informer integration\n- ✅ Request routing and reverse proxy capabilities\n- ✅ Concurrency limiting (max concurrent requests)\n- ✅ Metrics collection (request count, response time, active connections)\n- ✅ Middleware: logging, recovery, correlation ID, JWT auth\n- ✅ Health check endpoints: `/health/live`, `/health/ready`\n- ✅ API routes match specification: session creation, retrieval, invocation proxying\n\n#### Store Module (`pkg/store/`)\n- ✅ Unified `Store` interface defined\n- ✅ Redis and ValKey implementations present\n- ✅ Codec support (JSON, MsgPack)\n- ✅ Session storage and retrieval methods\n- ✅ Expiration tracking for garbage collection\n\n#### PicoD Module (`pkg/picod/`)\n- ✅ Code execution handler with timeout support\n- ✅ File operations: upload, download, list, delete\n- ✅ Workspace management with path sanitization\n- ✅ Authentication middleware\n- ✅ Kubernetes integration with status reporting\n- ✅ Informer-based resource monitoring\n\n#### Workload Manager (`pkg/workloadmanager/`)\n- ✅ Kubernetes custom controller architecture\n- ✅ AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resource management\n- ✅ API endpoints: `/v1/agent-runtime`, `/v1/code-interpreter`, `/v1/sessions/:sessionId`\n- ✅ Garbage collector for expired sessions\n- ✅ Store integration for session persistence\n\n#### Common Types (`pkg/common/types/`)\n- ✅ `SandboxInfo` structure matches documentation\n- ✅ Request/response types properly defined\n- ✅ Support for both AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter kinds\n- ✅ Proper error handling structures\n\n### API Contract Verification ✅\n\nThe implementation matches the documented API contracts:\n\n| API Endpoint | Doc Spec | Implementation | Status |\n|-------------|----------|---------------|---------|\n| `POST /v1/sessions/:namespace/:kind/:name` | ✅ | ✅ Router/handlers.go:120 | Match |\n| `GET /v1/sessions/:sessionID` | ✅ | ✅ Router/handlers.go:126 | Match |\n| `ANY /v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | ✅ | ✅ Router/server.go:133 | Match |\n| `ANY /v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | ✅ | ✅ Router/server.go:138 | Match |\n| `GET /health/live` | ✅ | ✅ Router/server.go:113 | Match |\n| `GET /health/ready` | ✅ | ✅ Router/server.go:114 | Match |\n\n### Test Status ❌\n\n**Tests are NOT passing** - Multiple compilation errors:\n\n#### Router Tests\n- ❌ `server_test.go:166`: kubernetes.Interface implementation mismatch\n- ❌ Multiple test files have compilation issues\n\n#### Store Tests  \n- ❌ `singleton_test.go`: Undefined `NewStore` function\n- ❌ Multiple test files cannot compile\n\n#### PicoD Tests\n- ❌ Duplicate test function declarations\n- ❌ Struct field mismatches (FileInfo, Server)\n- ❌ Type conversion errors\n\n#### Workload Manager Tests\n- ❌ Undefined functions: `statusConditionsEqual`, `podSpecsEqual`, `convertEnvVars`\n- ❌ Configuration field mismatches in controllerruntime.Options\n- ❌ Store interface method mismatch\n\n### Build Status ❌\n\n```bash\ngo build ./...\n```\n\nMultiple compilation errors across:\n- Workload manager controller/reconciler (undefined functions, unknown fields)\n- Handler (store interface mismatch)\n- Client-go (deprecated/missing Kubernetes API fields)\n\n### Summary\n\n**Requirements Met**: ✅ **Documentation** is complete and matches AR-043 specifications\n\n**API Contracts**: ✅ **Implemented correctly** and match documented behavior\n\n**Tests**: ❌ **Failing** - Multiple test files have compilation errors\n\n**Code Quality**: ⚠️ **Issues found** - Build fails with compilation errors in workload manager and client-go modules\n\n**Overall Status**: **Documentation and architecture are solid, but implementation has quality issues preventing tests from passing and code from building.**\n\n### Recommendations\n\n1. **Fix test compilation errors** - Address undefined functions and struct mismatches\n2. **Update Kubernetes client-go** - Fix deprecated API usage\n3. **Complete workload manager implementation** - Implement missing utility functions\n4. **Add integration tests** - Verify end-to-end functionality\n5. **Fix build issues** - Ensure all modules compile successfully","time":{"start":1775900788352,"end":1775900788352}}}
